Projects

Source: vignettes/projects.Rmd
projects.Rmd
library(basecamper)

Retrieve all Projects

projects <- basecamper::basecamp_projects()

Inspecting Projects

Print

Summary

Summary method for a projects object will return a tibble with company name associated with the project, with the id and name of the project.

Retrieve all Projects

Choose a project

(METRUM <- summary(projects)[[2,'id']])
#> [1] "8514810"
project <- basecamper::basecamp_project(METRUM)

Inspecting a Project

Print

Printing the project object will return basic meta information

project
#> QC help
#> ID: 8514810
#> Status: active
#> Company : Metrum Research Group
#> Create On: 2011-11-23
#> Last Changed: 2019-10-11T14:19:41Z
